</li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-36"><a href="#European_studies_and_discourse"><span class="tocnumber">9.4</span> <span class="toctext">European studies and discourse</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-37"><a href="#Symbolic_usage"><span class="tocnumber">9.5</span> <span class="toctext">Symbolic usage</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-38"><a href="#In_popular_culture"><span class="tocnumber">9.6</span> <span class="toctext">In popular culture</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-39"><a href="#See_also"><span class="tocnumber">10</span> <span class="toctext">See also</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-40"><a href="#Notes"><span class="tocnumber">11</span> <span class="toctext">Notes</span></a></li>
