<td>Mystical speculations, Philosophy
</td>
<td>Darsana, <a href="/wiki/Samkhya" title="Samkhya">Samkhya</a>, <a href="/wiki/Yoga_(philosophy)" title="Yoga (philosophy)">Yoga (philosophy)</a>, <a href="/wiki/Nyaya" title="Nyaya">Nyaya</a>, <a href="/wiki/Vaisheshika" title="Vaisheshika">Vaisheshika</a>, <a href="/wiki/Mimamsa" class="mw-redirect" title="Mimamsa">Mimamsa</a>, <a href="/wiki/Vedanta" title="Vedanta">Vedanta</a>, <a href="/wiki/Vaishnavism" title="Vaishnavism">Vaishnavism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Shaivism" title="Shaivism">Shaivism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Shaktism" title="Shaktism">Shaktism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Smarta_Tradition" class="mw-redirect" title="Smarta Tradition">Smarta Tradition</a> and others
</td>
<td><sup id="cite_ref-367" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-367">&#91;334&#93;</a></sup>
</td></tr>
