<li id="cite_note-FOOTNOTEThomas_Burrow2001v_&amp;_ch._1-25"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-FOOTNOTEThomas_Burrow2001v_&amp;_ch._1_25-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="#CITEREFThomas_Burrow2001">Thomas Burrow 2001</a>, pp.&#160;v &amp; ch. 1.</span>
