<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://sanskritdocuments.org/home.html">Sanskrit Documents</a>—Documents in ITX format of Upanishads, Stotras etc.</li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sacred-texts.com/hin/index.htm">Sanskrit texts at Sacred Text Archive</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cudl.lib.cam.ac.uk/collections/sanskrit">Sanskrit Manuscripts</a> in <a href="/wiki/Cambridge_Digital_Library" title="Cambridge Digital Library">Cambridge Digital Library</a></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.lexilogos.com/keyboard/sanskrit_devanagari.htm">Lexilogos Sanskrit Keyboard</a> for writing Sanskrit on a computer.</li></ul>
